article.description: Evan Wieck had 18 points as Navy narrowly beat American 60-56 in the Patriot League Conference Tourney quarterfinals on Thursday night.
article.headline: Wieck scores 18 to carry Navy past American 60-56
article.linkText: Wieck scores 18 to carry Navy past American 60-56
article.story: WASHINGTON -- Evan Wieck had 18 points as Navy narrowly beat American 60-56 in the Patriot League Conference Tourney quarterfinals on Thursday night. John Carter Jr. had seven rebounds for Navy (12-18). George Kiernan added nine rebounds. Sa'eed Nelson had 29 points for the Eagles (15-15). Stacy Beckton Jr. added nine rebounds.
